@page "/About"

<PageTitle>Badluck Achievements - About</PageTitle>

<div class="about-container">
    <h1>About Badluck Achievements</h1>

    <p>Welcome to <span class="highlight">Badluck Achievements</span>, your premier destination for in-depth gaming achievement analytics and tracking. We're passionate about gaming and the satisfaction that comes with unlocking achievements.</p>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>I created Badluck Achievements to help gamers understand their achievement hunting patterns, track progress in steam, and connect with fellow achievement enthusiasts. Our platform provides statistics, rarity tracking, and personalized recommendations to enhance your gaming experience.</p>

    <h2>Key Features</h2>
    <div class="feature-list">
        <div class="feature-item">
            <h3>Comprehensive Analytics</h3>
            <p>Track your achievement progress with detailed statistics and visualizations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
            <h3>Rarity Tracking</h3>
            <p>Discover how rare your achievements are compared to the global player base.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
            <h3>Personalized Recommendations</h3>
            <p>Get suggestions for games and achievements based on your play history.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
            <h3>Community Features</h3>
            <p>Compare score with friends and join achievement hunting challenges.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>About the Developer</h2>
    <p>Badluck Achievements was created by a solo developer passionate about gaming and data analytics. What started as a personal project to track achievements evolved into this platform to share with fellow gamers.</p>

